---
import { ArrowRight } from "lucide-react";
---

<section
  class="bg-background py-12 md:py-24 md:overflow-visible mt-10 md:mt-28"
>
  <div
    class="flex w-full flex-col items-center px-6 md:flex-row md:items-center md:gap-14 md:px-64"
  >
    <img
      src="/images/IglesiaJCV.png"
      alt="Fachada de la iglesia Jesús Camino de Vida en Callao"
      class="mx-auto h-128 w-85.25 rounded-[25px] object-cover shadow-[0_12px_30px_rgba(0,0,0,0.14)] md:-mt-12 md:mx-0 md:h-[1098px] md:w-[726px] md:shrink-0"
      loading="lazy"
      decoding="async"
    />

    <div class="mt-11 w-full max-w-140 text-left md:mt-0">
      <h2
        id="ven-y-conoce-title"
        class="font-heading text-[52px] font-medium leading-[1.02] tracking-tight md:text-[69px]"
      >
        Ven y Conoce
      </h2>

      <p class="mt-3.5 text-[20px] leading-[1.22] text-foreground/85 md:mt-6">
        Soñamos con un movimiento que no se queda, sino que va, que cruza
        fronteras y corazones para compartir el evangelio de Jesús. Un
        movimiento donde cada paso es una oportunidad para anunciar Su amor, y
        cada vida transformada se convierte en un testimonio vivo del poder de
        Dios.
      </p>

      <div class="mt-3.5 space-y-1 text-[20px] leading-[1.3] md:mt-7.5">
        <p><span class="font-bold">Domingos:</span> 7:00 a.m & 6:00 p.m</p>
        <p>
          <span class="font-bold">Lugar:</span> Parque Ricardo Palma 144 - Callao
        </p>
      </div>

      <div
        class="mt-7.5 flex w-full flex-nowrap items-center gap-3 md:mt-6 md:w-auto md:gap-5"
      >
        <a
          href="#"
          class="inline-flex h-11 min-w-42.5 items-center justify-center rounded-xl bg-primary px-6 text-base font-bold text-primary-foreground transition-colors hover:bg-primary/90 md:h-12 md:min-w-40 md:px-8 md:text-xl"
        >
          ¿Eres Nuevo?
        </a>

        <a
          href="#"
          class="group inline-flex max-w-47.5 flex-none items-center gap-1 self-center border-b-2 border-black px-0 pb-1 text-[13px] text-foreground transition-all duration-200 md:max-w-none md:gap-3 md:text-[14px]
           hover:rounded-2xl hover:border-transparent hover:bg-black hover:px-6 hover:py-3 hover:text-white
           focus-visible:rounded-2xl focus-visible:border-transparent focus-visible:bg-black focus-visible:px-6 focus-visible:py-3 focus-visible:text-white"
        >
          <span class="leading-[1.1] md:leading-tight"
            >Conoce mas sobre nosotros</span
          >
          <ArrowRight
            className="h-5 w-5 stroke-[2.5] transition-transform duration-200 group-hover:translate-x-0.5 group-active:translate-x-0.5 group-focus-visible:translate-x-0.5"
          />
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
